3. 가설 검증¶

1) 농업종사자 비율이 낮을수록 1인당 GDP가 높을 것이다¶

  • , .
nadropped_df = cutted_df[(cutted_df["GDP per capita (current US$)"].isna() == False) & (cutted_df["Employment in agriculture (% of total employment) (modeled ILO estimate)"].isna()==False)]
  • .
fig = px.scatter(nadropped_df,x="Employment in agriculture (% of total employment) (modeled ILO estimate)", y="GDP per capita (current US$)",
                 animation_frame="year", animation_group="Country Name",
                 range_x=[0, 100], range_y=[100, 130000], log_y=True
 )
fig.show()

1 GDP .

2) 문해율이 낮을수록 영아사망률이 높을 것이다.¶

  • , .
nadropped_df = cutted_df[(cutted_df["Literacy rate, adult total (% of people ages 15 and above)"].isna() == False) & (cutted_df["Mortality rate, infant (per 1,000 live births)"].isna()==False)]
  • .
fig = px.scatter(nadropped_df,y="Mortality rate, infant (per 1,000 live births)", x="Literacy rate, adult total (% of people ages 15 and above)",
                 animation_frame="year", animation_group="Country Name",
                 range_x=[0, 100], range_y=[0, 200]
 )
fig.show()

.

3) 출생률이 낮을수록 성평등 등급이 높을 것이다.¶

  • , .
nadropped_df = cutted_df[(cutted_df["Birth rate, crude (per 1,000 people)"].isna() == False) & (cutted_df["CPIA gender equality rating (1=low to 6=high)"].isna()==False)]
  • .
fig = px.scatter(nadropped_df,y="CPIA gender equality rating (1=low to 6=high)", x="Birth rate, crude (per 1,000 people)",
                 animation_frame="year", animation_group="Country Name",
                 range_x=[5, 60], range_y=[0, 7]
 )
fig.show()
